N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2100.12 - Withdrawal from rental market

State Regulations

Nothing in this Subchapter shall be construed to require
any person to offer any housing accommodations for rent, but housing
accommodations already on the rental market may be withdrawn only after an
order is issued by the administrator under section
2104.9
of this Title, if such
withdrawal requires that a tenant be evicted from such
accommodations. Notes
